dn-cronsudo README
==================

This package supplies cron files for repeated tasks:

Daily
- download new BBC Radio podcasts for user 'david'
- update system clock
- update file database for 'locate' utility

Weekly
- update vim bundles for user 'david'

The package also provides sudoer files for /etc/sudoers.d/:

dn-pkg-manage
- enable ordinary user to run package management tools

dn-edit
- enable ordinary users to edit system files with (g)edit.

dn-filesys
- filesystem manipulation: (un)mounting and ejecting

dn-network
- raising network interfaces with ifup

dn-wireless
- wireless device management with bluetooth tools
